import React from 'react'
import { Head } from './Components/Head'
import { BrowserRouter, Route, Routes } from 'react-router-dom'
export const App = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/">Helloo</Route>
        <Route path="/Head">
          <Head />
        </Route>
      </Routes>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}
